---
// Solution.astro — 4 pillars of the Phronesis solution
---
<section class="section bg-radial-blue" id="product">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">✦ The Solution</div>
      <h2>Your AI's Black Box.<br/>Finally readable.</h2>
      <p>Phronesis sits passively alongside your AI agents, ingesting every decision as it happens and transforming raw telemetry into structured, legally defensible evidence.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- UVP statement -->
    <div class="uvp-banner">
      <div class="uvp-left">
        <div class="uvp-label mono">// Unique Value Proposition</div>
        <blockquote class="uvp-text">
          "Safely unblock your Agentic AI deployments. We translate unreadable AI telemetry
          into structured, chronological audit trails — giving you the forensic evidence required
          to confidently file a DORA or RBI incident report in <strong>under 4 hours.</strong>"
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="uvp-metrics">
        <div class="uvp-metric">
          <span class="metric-val">3s</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Evidence pack generation</span>
        </div>
        <div class="uvp-metric">
          <span class="metric-val">4h</span>
          <span class="metric-label">DORA/RBI window — covered</span>
        </div>
        <div class="uvp-metric">
          <span class="metric-val">0</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Code changes to your AI</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 4 pillars -->
    <div class="solution-grid">
      <!-- Pillar 1 -->
      <div class="solution-card card" id="solution-replay">
        <div class="solution-number">01</div>
        <div class="solution-icon">🎬</div>
        <h3>Forensic Reasoning Replay</h3>
        <p>Ingests standard OpenTelemetry traces and automatically translates them into a human-readable, chronological decision tree — step by step, in plain English.</p>
        <div class="solution-example">
          <div class="example-row">
            <span class="mono example-time">14:01:03</span>
            <span class="example-action">Agent started — FX Routing Workflow #4821</span>
          </div>
          <div class="example-row">
            <span class="mono example-time">14:01:04</span>
            <span class="example-action">Read: sanctions_list.pdf (cached, stale)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="example-row example-row--anomaly">
            <span class="mono example-time">14:01:05</span>
            <span class="example-action">⚠ Decision: Approved transfer based on stale data <span style="font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 2px 4px; background: rgba(245,158,11,0.2); border-radius: 4px; margin-left: 4px; display: inline-block;">Confidence: Moderate</span></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-regulation">
          <span class="badge badge-blue">SR 26-2 — Effective Challenge Evidence</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 2 -->
      <div class="solution-card card" id="solution-dora">
        <div class="solution-number">02</div>
        <div class="solution-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>1-Click DORA Evidence Pack</h3>
        <p>When an incident occurs, your CRO opens the dashboard, clicks one button, and receives a perfectly structured, regulator-ready PDF — not a frantic Slack thread.</p>
        <div class="solution-feature-list">
          <div class="feat-row">
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            <span>Chronological incident timeline</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-row">
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            <span>Root cause analysis — automated</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-row">
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            <span>DORA Article 19 required headers</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-row">
            <span class="feat-check">✓</span>
            <span>Cryptographic integrity hash</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-regulation">
          <span class="badge badge-amber">DORA Art. 19 / RBI Cyber Resilience</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 3 -->
      <div class="solution-card card" id="solution-ledger">
        <div class="solution-number">03</div>
        <div class="solution-icon">🔒</div>
        <h3>Context-Aware Append-Only Ledger</h3>
        <p>A high-velocity event-streaming backend that chains scattered agent traces into a single, tamper-evident system of record. The logs are immutable — just like a real flight recorder.</p>
        <div class="solution-architecture">
          <div class="arch-row">
            <div class="arch-node">Event Depot</div>
            <div class="arch-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="arch-node">Topology</div>
            <div class="arch-arrow">→</div>
            <div class="arch-node arch-node--highlight">PailState</div>
          </div>
          <div class="arch-detail">Hash-chained · Append-only · Tamper-evident</div>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-regulation">
          <span class="badge badge-cyan">SR 26-2 — System of Record</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pillar 4 -->
      <div class="solution-card card" id="solution-mirror">
        <div class="solution-number">04</div>
        <div class="solution-icon">🌐</div>
        <h3>Deploy Anywhere: Hosted or Air-Gapped</h3>
        <p>Your data, your rules. Choose a fully managed cloud for convenience, or deploy 100% on-premise behind your firewall. In our air-gapped mode, your sensitive telemetry never leaves your infrastructure.</p>
        <div class="solution-tiers">
          <div class="mirror-tier">
            <span class="tier-label">Cloud</span>
            <span class="tier-desc">Fully managed hosted option for rapid deployment</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mirror-tier">
            <span class="tier-label">In-House</span>
            <span class="tier-desc">100% air-gapped on-premise deployment</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mirror-tier" style="margin-top: 0.25rem; border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);">
            <span class="tier-label" style="color: var(--color-blue);">24x7 Support</span>
            <span class="tier-desc">We are always here to assist you, because you never know when you'll need us</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-regulation">
          <span class="badge badge-green">DPDPA & GDPR Data Sovereignty</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
/* UVP banner */
.uvp-banner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 2rem;
  align-items: center;
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--color-cyan);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}
.uvp-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.uvp-text {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--color-text);
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-style: italic;
  margin: 0;
}
.uvp-text strong { color: var(--color-cyan); font-style: normal; }
.uvp-metrics {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
  min-width: 140px;
}
.uvp-metric { text-align: right; }
.metric-val {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-cyan);
  display: block;
  line-height: 1;
}
.metric-label {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--color-text-dim);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
}

/* Solution grid */
.solution-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.solution-card {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  position: relative;
}

.solution-number {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--color-text-dim);
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
}
.solution-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; }
.solution-card h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; }
.solution-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; flex: 1; }

.solution-example {
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  padding: 0.75rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.4rem;
  font-size: 0.72rem;
}
.example-row { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: flex-start; }
.example-time { color: var(--color-text-dim); flex-shrink: 0; }
.example-action { color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.4; }
.example-row--anomaly .example-action { color: var(--color-amber); }

.solution-feature-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
.feat-row { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
.feat-check { color: var(--color-green); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; }

.solution-architecture { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.35); border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 0.75rem; }
.arch-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.arch-node {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  background: var(--color-surface-2);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
}
.arch-node--highlight { border-color: var(--color-cyan); color: var(--color-cyan); background: var(--color-cyan-dim); }
.arch-arrow { color: var(--color-text-dim); font-size: 0.8rem; }
.arch-detail { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); font-family: var(--font-mono); }

.solution-tiers { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
.mirror-tier {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.75rem;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
}
.tier-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--color-cyan);
  font-weight: 600;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.tier-desc { color: var(--color-text-muted); }

.solution-regulation { margin-top: auto; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .uvp-banner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .uvp-metrics { flex-direction: row; min-width: unset; }
  .uvp-metric { text-align: left; }
}
</style>
